sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant K8S as Kubernetes API
    participant Op as Llama Stack Operator
    participant Pod as Llama Stack Pod
    participant HF as Hugging Face Hub
    participant PVC as PVC Storage
    participant Ollama as Ollama/vLLM Backend
    participant Client

    Note over User,PVC: Flow 1: Model Download and Initialization
    User->>K8S: Create LlamaStackDistribution CR (6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3)
    K8S-->>User: 201 Created

    K8S->>Op: Watch event: LlamaStackDistribution created
    Op->>K8S: Create Deployment (6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3)
    K8S->>Pod: Start Llama Stack Pod
    Pod->>HF: Download model (443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3 API Token)
    HF-->>Pod: Model files
    Pod->>PVC: Store model (Local)
    Pod->>Ollama: Initialize backend (11434/TCP HTTP optional)
    Pod-->>Op: Pod ready

    Note over Client,Ollama: Flow 2: Inference Request (Internal)
    Client->>Pod: POST /v1/chat/completions (8000/TCP HTTP TLS 1.2+ API Key)
    Pod->>Ollama: Inference request (11434/TCP HTTP)
    Ollama->>Ollama: Generate response (GPU if vLLM)
    Ollama-->>Pod: Inference result
    Pod-->>Client: 200 OK completion response

    Note over User,Pod: Flow 3: Inference Request (External via Route)
    User->>Pod: POST /v1/chat/completions (443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+ API Key)
    Pod->>Ollama: Inference request (11434/TCP HTTP)
    Ollama->>Ollama: Generate response
    Ollama-->>Pod: Inference result
    Pod-->>User: 200 OK completion response
